rows.label: xs04500100_MSG0001
rows.name: Looks like the Life Point is up ahead, but[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04500100_MSG0002
rows.name: We're going over this rocky mountain, meh!?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04500100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Nnngh, impossible, meh!
For frail little Tatsu, it's totally impossible, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04500100_MSG0005
rows.name:
But, it's not just Tatsu.
It really does seem impossible to cross this rocky mountain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04500100_MSG0006
rows.name: Right. It'll be a bit of a detour, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04500100_MSG0007
rows.name: Let's try going around that way.[ST:wait ]
